description:
In core/actions.pyx:357-360, raise bid mask generation loops through all 19 possible raises even when player can't afford higher bids. Once a player can't afford a bid, all higher amounts are also unaffordable.

Current:
```cython
for bid_offset in range(AUCTION_CAP - 1):
    new_bid = face_value + bid_offset + 1
    if new_bid > current_bid and new_bid <= player_cash:
        mask[...] = 1.0
```

Better:
```cython
for bid_offset in range(AUCTION_CAP - 1):
    new_bid = face_value + bid_offset + 1
    if new_bid > current_bid:
        if new_bid <= player_cash:
            mask[...] = 1.0
        else:
            break  # Can't afford this or higher
```

Minor optimization (AUCTION_CAP is only 20).
